Description: Monochrome KDE base for error.os
 A full-fledged dark and grey themed KDE desktop foundation. This package
 forms the expressive core of error.os, combining visual minimalism with
 modular intent. It contains Bash configuration, Monochrome KDE Plasma 6
 theme, Pre-configured yakuake terminal, Kvantum Qt6 styling, Custom
 Plymouth boot splash, SDDM display manager configuration, a minimal
 version of Bibata cursor theme, GTK2/GTK3 integration, and essential
 runtime dependencies.

